Package com.dod.models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Character
    A Character is a fictional entity that moves around the game world.
    Map
    A Map stores a 2-dimensional grid of Tiles.
    Match
    Represents a match
    Player
    A Player represents the user that is in control of the game client A Player can sign in with a username or password A Player has a level and a password salt A Player's password is always hashed
    Point
    Bean class for storing a point (or vertex) in the map.
    Score
    A Score stores the points a Player achieved when they completed a Match.
    Tile
    A Tile represents single tile on the grid that is the Map A Tile has a Type that indicates whether it is eg a wall, floor, coin or exit tile.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MatchState
    The state of a Match.
    TileType
    The type of a tile, i.e is this tile a wall, floor or something else.
